### 创建一个工厂Bean

我们可以创建一个实现了`FactoryBean<FXMLLoader>`的类。在这个类中，您可以注入`ApplicationContext`，因为工厂bean会在ApplicationContext准备好之后被实例化，所以不会遇到之前提到的顺序问题。

```java
import javafx.fxml.FXMLLoader;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean;
import org.springframework.context.ApplicationContext;
import org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware;
import org.springframework.core.io.Resource;

public class FXMLLoaderFactoryBean implements FactoryBean<FXMLLoader>, ApplicationContextAware {

    private ApplicationContext applicationContext;
    private Resource fxmlLocation;

    public void setFxmlLocation(Resource fxmlLocation) {
        this.fxmlLocation = fxmlLocation;
    }

    @Override
    public void setApplicationContext(ApplicationContext applicationContext) {
        this.applicationContext = applicationContext;
    }

    @Override
    public FXMLLoader getObject() throws Exception {
        FXMLLoader loader = new FXMLLoader(fxmlLocation.getURL());
        loader.setControllerFactory(applicationContext::getBean);
        return loader;
    }

    @Override
    public Class<?> getObjectType() {
        return FXMLLoader.class;
    }

    @Override
    public boolean isSingleton() {
        return false; // 根据您加载FXML是否需要独立实例来决定
    }
}
```

### 注册工厂Bean

然后，您可以在您的`BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor`实现中使用这个工厂bean来注册您的`FXMLLoader`实例：

```java
import org.springframework.beans.factory.support.BeanDefinitionBuilder;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.support.BeanDefinitionRegistry;
import org.springframework.core.io.Resource;
import org.springframework.core.io.support.PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver;

public void registerFxmlLoaders(BeanDefinitionRegistry registry) throws IOException {
    PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver resolver = new PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver();
    // 假设yourFxmlLocationPattern是您用来匹配FXML文件的位置模式
    Resource[] resources = resolver.getResources("yourFxmlLocationPattern");
    for (Resource resource : resources) {
        BeanDefinitionBuilder builder = BeanDefinitionBuilder.genericBeanDefinition(FXMLLoaderFactoryBean.class);
        builder.addPropertyValue("fxmlLocation", resource);
        registry.registerBeanDefinition(resource.getFilename(), builder.getBeanDefinition());
    }
}
```

这种方法解决了`ApplicationContextAware`在`BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor`阶段之后被调用的顺序问题，因为它把`FXMLLoader`实例的创建延后到工厂bean实际需要被创建的时刻，而此时`ApplicationContext`已经是可用的了。这样，您就可以在工厂bean中安全地使用`ApplicationContext`了。

